<subSubSection id="C358655E860C6B2BFAE087B3FB85FAAE" lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="94" pageId="30" pageNumber="93" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BFD36D5860C6B2BFAE087B3FE62FE5E" blockId="30.[1289,2272,3015,3192]" lastBlockId="31.[223,1207,415,1333]" lastPageId="31" lastPageNumber="94" pageId="30" pageNumber="93">Description. Shell minute, high-spired, anomphalous. Protoconch of IV! whorls, deviated. Teleoconch of 5 to 6 smooth, moderately convex whorls, with faint growth lines. Aperture circular to oval, lips thin, no columellar fold.</paragraph>
